cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL

The paper presents a method for 3D object detection that leverages both image and 3D point cloud information. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on object detection and uses deep learning techniques, cs.CV and cs.RO are the most likely sub-categories.
